          <para styleclass="SeeAlso"><text styleclass="SeeAlso" translate="true">See also : </text><image src="MD-Globe-www-24.png" scale="100.00%" styleclass="Image Caption" style="font-size:7pt; vertical-align:sub;" figurelistinclude="0"></image><text styleclass="SeeAlso" translate="true">&#32;</text><link displaytype="text" defaultstyle="true" type="weblink" href="http://mechdesigner.support/index.htm?tutorial-9-asymmetrical-motions.htm" target="_blank" styleclass="Body Text" translate="true">Tutorial 9: Asymmetrical Motions.</link></para>
